overview: This is lesbian drama like no other! There's no drama like lesbian drama. These girls have fiery tempers and know just how to work out the tension. GirlFriends Films explores these explosive dramas in four outstanding lesbian scenes! Featuring Misa F, Lily Labeau, Nadia Noir, Nicole Moore, Prinzess, Rozen Debowe and Zoe Britton!
title: Lesbian PsychoDramas 15
